{
  "stem": "210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I got off the train, there were probably, maybe a quarter of the people who were in the train were dead because it took about three days.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and it was such a chaos with the SS, with the dogs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with the people that were helping them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was such a chaos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't know where you're going, didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just hit you with these-- out, out from the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they-- you came to a certain place, and they segregated you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You go here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You go there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we still-- you know, we didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we went through this-- they told us, they took to a one big barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said we should put all our stuff down there and take off all our clothes and just put it in a pile.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we walked out from there naked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then, we were in a-- in a row where they cut off our hair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when we came out of the other side without hair, I didn't recognize anybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us-- you know, and we started, you know, calling names, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we didn't know who we were anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those two, the mother with the two daughters were next to me, and we tried to be together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those other two girls I couldn't find anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were sitting outside in Auschwitz for about half a night, or-- naked in a-- in like, a-- in a field.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the morning, they assigned us to a barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there were people in there already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, let's say, when there were, where there were three, they put one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everyone had to be four people in each one of these.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
